3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - Maximal cliques are a fundamental concept in social and information networks, and the paper deals with mining them from an uncertain graph. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper presents an algorithm to enumerate maximal cliques in an uncertain graph, which involves computational techniques that are closely related to machine learning.
